{"tid":2038972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共搞送中條例會唔會係因為孟晚舟?","createTime":"2020-05-27T20:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T22:32:54.000Z","uid":138381,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa14aeba0a48ba7ffc5215c69cf3b6e7d7c38f20","tid":2038972,"uid":138381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T20:16:23.000Z","msg":"其實中共搞送中條例會唔會係因為呢條友<br />\n想用呢招引渡在港美國重要人士對付返美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(因為加拿大引渡左佢去俾美國)<br />\n咁岩陳同佳案 就打算順個靚勢立法<br />\n點知俾人當左目的做侵犯香港自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地本身諗住香港慢慢贏就算 反正滲透得咁西利<br />\n結果搞成咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真如果唔係咁樣<br />\n我諗唔明點解中共會咁突然 咁明目張膽搞香港<br />\n搞到大量港豬全面覺醒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2654175/%E3%80%90%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E3%80%91%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E7%9C%8B%E6%87%82%20%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E6%A1%88%E5%A7%8B%E6%9C%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2654175%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25AD%259F%25E6%2599%259A%25E8%2588%259F%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E6%2587%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2585%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%2587%2582%2520%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25AD%259F%25E6%2599%259A%25E8%2588%259F%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%25A7%258B%25E6%259C%25AB&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32ctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=131814e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2654175/%E3%80%90%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E3%80%91%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E7%9C%8B%E6%87%82%20%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E6%A1%88%E5%A7%8B%E6%9C%AB</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月10日：中方以危害國家安全為由拘捕加國前外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig）及商人斯帕弗（Michael Spavor），被指報復孟晚舟被加方拘捕<br />\n<br />\n可見垃圾中共對呢件事好上心好想報仇"},{"pid":"234145cdd1fc55b5044767d